function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	idClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(idGulyas)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idClone) then
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idClone, marker_Gulyas_Table, "npc_walk", true)
		Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idClone, anim_Inspect)
		Hydra.QActorWait(idClone, 5.0)
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idClone)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idClone, idGulyas, "npc_walk", true)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idClone, 0.0)
	end
end
